Syntax: game <message>

Sends a message on the game channel, which is visible to all connected
players. The channel is prefixed with a colored [GAME] tag.

Example:
  game Anyone up for the dungeon run tonight?

To disable or enable receiving game channel messages, use the CHANNELS
command to toggle the channel.

This channel is intended for in-game discussion such as grouping, trade
announcements, and general game-related conversation.

See also: channels gossip newbie ooc invasion
